Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:16:02.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の私は　あなたの\N作ろうとしている物語の→
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.93,0:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this me be the heroine \Nof the story you want to make?
